261  double getTotalHeat() {
262  const double tempDiff = dischargeTemperature - initialTemperature;
263  const double hgas = (1.0 - percentVapor) * feedRate * specificHeatGas * tempDiff;
264  const double hvapor = percentVapor * feedRate * specificHeatVapor * tempDiff;
265 
266  // heatReact ignored when exothermic
267  double heatReact = 0.0;
268  if (thermicReactionType == LoadChargeMaterial::ThermicReactionType::ENDOTHERMIC) {
269  heatReact =feedRate * percentReacted * reactionHeat;
270  }
271 
272  totalHeat = hgas + hvapor + heatReact + additionalHeat;
273  return totalHeat;
274  }
